metadata.name: Serenity and Capsizing in Venice
metadata.description:
A peaceful Venetian gondola ride

Moments before nearly capsizing

Taken on iPhone 6 | Venice, Italy | June 2017

A fellow passenger kept hastily changing seats and almost tipped the boat over in the process

Our gondolier’s skills and expertise kept us afloat, but he was not the least bit enthused

Would’ve been quite the unique Italian experience

Artist: MartianChief

Link to thread detailing how I edited this photo: https://twitter.com/MartianChief/status/1605039377977065472?s=20
